  "prompt": "What are the scientific names for domestic animals, for example, cows and horses?",
  "response": "Certainly! Here are the scientific names for some common domestic animals:\n\n- Cows: Bos taurus\n- Horses: Equus ferus caballus\n- Dogs: Canis lupus familiaris\n- Cats: Felis catus\n- Chickens: Gallus gallus domesticus\n- Pigs: Sus scrofa domesticus\n- Sheep: Ovis aries\n- Goats: Capra aegagrus hircus\n\nThese names are used in scientific contexts to precisely identify and classify these animals.",
